    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Refers to the style and culture of the members of the Songhees Nation, a First Nation band of Lekwungen people (a Coast Salish subgroup). At one point, the term 'Songhees' was used for all Lekwungen people, but now refers to those who are members of the Songhees Nation. </Note_Text>
